text: Honnedaga Brook is a stream in the Adirondack Mountains of the U.S. state of New York. It starts at Honnedaga Lake and flows into West Canada Creek about upstream of Nobleboro, New York. ==References== Category:Rivers of New York (state) Category:Rivers of Hamilton County, New York Category:Rivers of Herkimer County, New York
